about.summary: nbconvert preprocessor for converting DataFrames to markdown.

name: nbconvert-utils
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "nbconvert-utils" %}
{% set version = "0.6" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name | replace("-", "_") }}/{{ name | replace("-", "_") }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6ba9bc16092aa3a9f89e1df1a4f6c2f372ea2d5067062ff5743753cedaa5de8d

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
    - nbconvert
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - nbconvert

test:
  imports:
    - nbconvert_utils

about:
  home: https://github.com/greenape/nbconvert_utils
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "nbconvert preprocessor for converting DataFrames to markdown."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - apcamargo
